<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.305712>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Nematocysts of Egmundella producta (G. O. Sars, 1874), alcohol preserved material in 50 % lactic acid, same scale for all images. (A-B) Undischarged large haplonemes. (C) Undischarged isorhiza capsules. (D) Unidentified small capsules. (E) Discharged large haploneme with barbs on thread. (F) Discharged large haploneme without apparent barbs on thread." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/305712/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

